INSERT INTO librarian.lmsinno_document (title, document_id, description, publisher, year, type, price, is_reference, copies_available, cover, date_added, is_bestseller) VALUES ('Bitcoin Cryptocurrency Secrets!', 500, 'Introduction The Cryptocurrency Boom Is A Once-In-A-Lifetime Opportunity! Have you been wondering how all these average people are profiting from bitcoin? Are you tired of all the confusing information on how crypto-currencies actually work? Countless people just like you are in the same boat but thatâs only because they donât know the SECRETS to profiting from bitcoin. To most people, Bitcoin can seem like a financial concept made in a parallel universe. Yes, itâs a very complex and complicated concept, but it doesnât mean itâs impossible to learn it. When you think about it, many people started off with no idea about bitcoins and how it worked. But look at them now, theyâre probably investing left and right in various cryptocurrencies like pros and possibly profiting very nicely as well! So, in this guide, weâll try to simplify how Bitcoin works and all your questions and concerns will be answered, step by step. Learn to capitalize on the stock opportunity of a lifetime: Cryptocurrencies. If you make the right moves, you could find yourself jumping for joy on top of an enormous pile of cash. Ready or not, a growing number of economies, banks, and billionaires are backing these new forms of tender. Once you understand how easy it is to profit from cryptocurrencies, itâs easy to see why the cryptocurrency market is preparing to take off and the only time to buy is now. Just one investment could soon put you in a new class of âcryptocurrency millionaires.â Now you can discover the secrets, and simple steps to follow inside the "Bitcoin Cryptocurrency Secrets" home study course starting today. If you don''t invest in cryptocurrency right now, you could regret it for the rest of your life. With "Bitcoin Cryptocurrency Secrets", you are