the first newly created crypto-currency to be tested on the open market, has a wide degree of variability in price, and is recognized by merchants worldwide. Buy Now; this book will only be available for a limited time!', 'CreateSpace', 2018, 0, 1800, 0, 0, 'https://books.google.com/books/content?id=pu0PrgEACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=2', '2018-02-03', 0);
